N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 14 ยง 819.13 - Sunset

State Regulations
(a) Notwithstanding
any other provision of this Title, Part 819 will no longer be in effect after

February 28, 2026. Operating certificates issued pursuant to this Part will
have no force and effect after February 28, 2026. (b) Providers that intend to continue
providing the services currently authorized under this Part will need to obtain
operating certificates under other applicable Parts of this Title, such as 14
NYCRR Part
820, on or before February 28, 2026. Notes
